6">hard</span> <span begin="24.866" end="25.136">to</span> <span begin="25.190" end="25.803">brea</span><span begin="25.803" end="25.865">the</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我被桎梏在这无形的悲伤里 喘不过气</span></p><p begin="25.865" end="28.790" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.865" end="26.044">I</span> <span begin="26.101" end="26.430">gave</span> <span begin="26.430" end="26.753">up</span> <span begin="26.753" end="27.028">eve</span><span begin="27.028" end="27.182">ry</span><span begin="27.182" end="27.831">thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">曾经为此放弃一切</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="27.938" end="28.790"><span begin="27.938" end="28.194">(Eve</span><span begin="28.194" end="28.364">ry</span><span begin="28.364" end="28.790">thing)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一切</span></span></p><p begin="28.526" end="32.180" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="28.526" end="28.791">And</span> <span begin="28.791" end="28.891">I</span> <span begin="28.891" end="29.608">slow</span> <span begin="29.969" end="30.584">fall</span> <span begin="30.584" end="30.902">down</span> <span begin="30.902" end="31.239">to</span> <span begin="31.239" end="31.376">the</span> <span begin="31.376" end="32.180">floor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我缓缓坠向地面</span></p><p begin="33.020" end="35.236" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.020" end="33.311">Life</span> <span begin="33.311" end="33.692">was</span> <span begin="33.692" end="33.980">es</span><span begin="33.980" end="34.567">ca</span><span begin="34.567" end="34.935">ping</span> <span begin="34.935" end="35.236">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">眼睁睁看着生命从我眼前溜走</span></p><p begin="35.500" end="37.646" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="35.500" end="35.706">I</span> <span begin="35.782" end="36.109">could</span><span begin="36.109" end="36.268">n&apos;t</span> <span begin="36.268" end="36.728">find</span> <span begin="36.728" end="36.951">my</span><span begin="36.951" end="37.646">self</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我迷失了自己 如堕烟海</span></p><p begin="37.895" end="40.277" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.895" end="38.238">&apos;Til</span> <span begin="38.238" end="38.459">it</span> <span begin="38.507" end="38.888">was</span> <span begin="38.888" end="39.354">all</span> <span begin="39.740" end="40.277">lost</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在我失去一切之前</span></p></div><div begin="40.319" end="58.776" itunes:songPart="PreChorus"><p begin="40.319" end="41.704" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.319" end="40.648">Not</span> <span begin="40.648" end="40.950">a</span><span begin="40.950" end="41.220">ny</span><span begin="41.220" end="41.704">more</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我要勇敢地去把这一切拿回来</span></p><p begin="42.310" end="47.513" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.310" end="42.488">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="42.488" end="42.745">hold</span><span begin="42.745" end="42.928">ing</span> <span begin="42.928" end="43.066">on</span> <span begin="43.066" end="43.330">to</span> <span begin="43.330" end="43.507">all</span> <span begin="43.507" end="43.679">the</span> <span begin="43.679" end="43.984">pie</span><span begin="43.984" end="44.361">ces</span> <span begin="44.361" end="44.737">of</span> <span begin="44.737" end="44.910">my</span> <span begin="44.910" end="45.348">heart&apos;s</span> <span begin="45.348" end="45.588">de</span><span begin="45.588" end="46.108">bris</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">咬紧牙关 握紧我那支离破碎的心</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="45.840" end="47.409"><span begin="45.840" end="45.955">(Of</span> <span begin="45.955" end="46.095">my</span> <span begin="46.095" end="46.625">heart&apos;s</span> <span begin="46.625" end="46.845">de</span><span begin="46.845" end="47.409">bris)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我那支离破碎的心</span></span></p><p begin="47.332" end="49.080" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="47.332" end="47.847">&apos;Til</span> <span begin="47.847" end="48.191">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="48.191" end="49.080">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">直到最后一刻</span></p><p begin="50.326" end="57.016" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.326" end="50.986">I&apos;ll,</span> <span begin="51.959" end="52.184">I&apos;ll</span> <span begin="52.184" end="52.451">pull</span> <span begin="52.451" end="52.592">it</span> <span begin="52.592" end="52.744">to</span><span begin="52.744" end="53.046">geth</span><span begin="53.046" end="53.190">er</span> <span begin="53.190" end="53.433">and</span> <span begin="53.433" end="53.782">fix</span> <span begin="53.782" end="53.957">my</span><span begin="53.957" end="54.429">self</span> <span begin="54.429" end="54.628">e</span><span begin="54.628" end="55.023">ven</span><span begin="55.023" end="55.276">tual</span><span begin="55.276" end="55.990">ly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我会将它一一拼凑 最后不药而愈</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="55.780" end="57.016"><span begin="55.780" end="55.886">(E</span><span begin="55.886" end="56.103">ven</span><span begin="56.202" end="56.526">tual</span><span begin="56.526" end="57.016">ly)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">终会不药而愈</span></span></p><p begin="56.835" end="58.776" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.835" end="57.029">I</span> <span begin="57.029" end="57.569">know</span> <span begin="57.569" end="57.921">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="57.921" end="58.776">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我知道这是属于我的</span></p></div><div begin="59.128" end="1:18.424" itunes:songPart="Chorus"><p begin="59.128" end="1:01.566" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.128" end="59.246">I</span> <span begin="59.246" end="59.720">found</span> <span begin="59.720" end="1:0